creator: Julia Caroline Dorr
description:
LibriVox recording of Later Poems by Julia Caroline Dorr.
Read in English by Sonia; Jael Baldwin; Julia Niedermaier; Newgatenovelist; Diana Schmidt; Sue Castor; Leonard Wilson; Rachel; Geralizze
This is the last volume in Julia Caroline Dorr's collected poems, the Later Poems. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
